rows.label: tlk400905_msg0001
rows.name: So what were you wanting to ask?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0002
rows.name:
Tora want to know if somebody bought
certain parts in large quantity or took
them to somebody.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0003
rows.name: When you say "certain parts"...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0004
rows.name:
There quite many variety.
Tora list them one after another,
so if any rings bell, please say.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0005
rows.name: Really? We're doing this again?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0006
rows.name: Tetra-Circle!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0007
rows.name: Snake Joint!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0008
rows.name: Black Ash!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0009
rows.name:
Hold it! I do have some info
on that last one.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0010
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh?! Over already?!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0011
rows.name: Masterpon look disappointed...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0012
rows.name: All right!

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0013
rows.name: Please, tell us the details.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0014
rows.name:
This old guy said he had a regular
customer purchasing Black Ash.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0015
rows.name:
Pretty large-scale stuff, from the
sounds of it. He was bragging about
how he'd be rolling in cash for a while.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0016
rows.name:
Black Ash is key mineral used as
shielding agent in ether furnace.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0017
rows.name: Sounds like we've got our guy.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0018
rows.name:
Do you know where we can find
this old guy?

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0019
rows.name: Hmmmmm...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0020
rows.name:
Now, isn't that odd.
I can't seem to recall.

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0021
rows.name:
Maybe if you bought something,
it might jog my memory...

rows.label: tlk400905_msg0022
rows.name: Why, you little...
